headline: E.l.f. Beauty Expands Global Footprint With Sephora
summary: The beauty brand strengthens its retail presence with Sephora in the Middle East, Dollar General in the U.S. and rising international sales, while navigating tariffs.

headline: Tree Hut Unmasks 'Eerie-Sistible' Fall Line to Kick Off the Spookiest Season Yet
summary: With Summer-ween in full swing, Tree Hut, America's No. 1 Body Scrub brand, is embracing the moment with the launch of its limited-edition Glow Potion Collection. This Halloween-inspired release blends nostalgic packaging with indulgent skincare, pairing fan-favorite product formats with festive new scents. The collection includes four spooky scents that are sure to bewitch consumers' body care routine – Sweet Punkin, Meyow, Frankenshine, and Scare Glow.

headline: Saje Natural Wellness Expands Retail Presence With Launch in First National Retailer, Ulta Beauty
summary: Saje Natural Wellness, a leader in North America for 100% plant- powered essential-oil remedies, today announced Ulta Beauty as the brand's first-ever national retail partner. The brand's bestsellers are now available in 200+ Ulta Beauty stores across the U.S, as well as online at ulta.com.
